  "id": "019d2e21-4ae6-7a22-bbf6-bd2d330809e1",
  "content": "# Forgetting Policies — Decisions (March 2026)\n\n## Two Policies for v1\n\n### 1. Inactivity-based (primary)\nForce entry to Cold if last_accessed exceeds max_inactive_days, regardless of composite score.\nDefault: 90 days. Per-type overrides: Episodic=14d, Decisional=365d, Procedural=180d, Structural=disabled.\n\n### 2. Budget-based (capacity)\nPer-scope cap on total entries. When exceeded, rank by retention_score, force bottom entries to Cold.\nDefault: 10,000 per scope.\n\nAge-based policy deferred — redundant with power-law decay function for v1.\n\n## Config Hierarchy\nGlobal defaults → per-type overrides → per-scope overrides (most specific wins).\n\n## Pinning\n- Explicit: `pinned: bool` field, skips all forgetting, requires manual unpin\n- Auto-protection (prevents Cold→Forgotten only, not demotion):\n  - memory_type == Structural\n  - HEAD of supersession chain (not superseded by anything)\n  - inbound_edges >= 5\n  - content_role == \"decision\" AND confidence >= 0.9",
  "source_version": "mcp",
